  "texts": [
    "Accessibility: Metagenomic data should be accessible to researchers using standardized protocols, such as hypertext transfer protocol (HTTP) or file transfer protocol (FTP).",
    "This ensures that researchers can access the data regardless of their computing environment.",
    "Interoperability: Metagenomic data should be stored in a format that is compatible with different learning algorithms and tools.",
    "This allows researchers to easily use the data to train and evaluate machine learning models.",
    "Reusability: Metagenomic data should be released with clear and accessible data usage licenses."
  ],
